                "notes": "Installed spire-server…\n\n1. Get the currently registered SPIFFE entries from the server:\n\n  kubectl exec -n megamart-cloud-tier spire-cloud-server-0 -c spire-server -- \\\n    spire-server entry show\n\nInstalled spire…\n\nInstalled spire-agent…\n\nSPIFFE OIDC discovery provider installed…\n\nSPIFFE CSI Driver installed…\n",
